  "text": "Step 1 (BFS traversal). Algorithm 3 employs level-synchronous BFS to grow an alternating BFS forest until the frontier F becomes empty. We use the direction-optimizing BFS algorithm [CITATION_1] that dynamically selects between top-down and bottom-up traversals based on the frontier size. ",
